headline: Friday's big stock stories: What’s likely to move the market in the next trading session
summary: The S&P 500 rose on Thursday, snapping a four-day string of losses after a softer-than-expected consumer inflation reading for November.

headline: D.R. Horton, Inc. to Release 2026 First Quarter Earnings on January 20, 2026
summary: ARLINGTON, Texas, December 18, 2025--D.R. Horton announced that the Company will release financial results for its first quarter ended December 31, 2025 on Tuesday, January 20, 2026.
